  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.contemporist.com/the-5-ceramics-of-italy-2025-tile-trends-that-are-shaping-interiors/\"\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blue-penny-tile-bathroom-240525-1039-01.jpg\" alt=\"This bold blue bathroom showcases sleek penny tile from floor to tub surround, creating a seamless and modern spa vibe. The matte blue fixtures and chrome chair complete the minimalist look with high-impact style.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blue-penny-tile-bathroom-240525-1039-01.jpg 1600w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blue-penny-tile-bathroom-240525-1039-01-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blue-penny-tile-bathroom-240525-1039-01-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blue-penny-tile-bathroom-240525-1039-01-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blue-penny-tile-bathroom-240525-1039-01-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eCoriandoli by Appiani\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eFresh from the floors of \u003ca href=\"https://www.coverings.com\"\u003eCoverings 2025\u003c/a\u003e in Orlando, \u003ca href=\"https://www.ceramica.info/\"\u003eCeramics of Italy\u003c/a\u003e has just unveiled its Spring-Summer 2025 Tile Trend Report, and it’s brimming with energy, craftsmanship, and soulful design. This year, Italian ceramic and porcelain tile is rewriting the rules of surfaces. It’s not just about finishes and formats anymore; it’s about feeling.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eFrom sculptural forms to emotion-evoking palettes, these five top trends are setting a new standard for what tile can do in the modern home and beyond.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003e1. Kaleidoscope of Color\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e2025’s tiles come dressed in every shade of expression. Think terracotta reds, sun-washed yellows, Mediterranean blues, sage greens, and dusty pinks, each one carefully chosen to evoke emotion and tell a story. Italian brands are leaning into rich color blocking and full-room “color drenching,” where spaces are enveloped top to bottom in a single tone.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2430\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bubble-yellow-tile-240525-1040-01.jpg\" alt=\"Bold and playful, this room uses yellow bubble tiles to create a statement wall that radiates optimism. The soft curves of the tiles give a retro pop-art vibe, perfect for a small powder room with personality.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bubble-yellow-tile-240525-1040-01.jpg 1600w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bubble-yellow-tile-240525-1040-01-940x1428.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bubble-yellow-tile-240525-1040-01-800x1215.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bubble-yellow-tile-240525-1040-01-768x1166.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bubble-yellow-tile-240525-1040-01-1011x1536.jpg 1011w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bubble-yellow-tile-240525-1040-01-1348x2048.jpg 1348w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eForever Color by CIR Ceramiche\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/dusty-pink-tile-240525-1040-01.jpg\" alt=\"These dusty pink tiles deliver a warm, modern look with a hint of vintage charm.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/dusty-pink-tile-240525-1040-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/dusty-pink-tile-240525-1040-01-940x940.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/dusty-pink-tile-240525-1040-01-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/dusty-pink-tile-240525-1040-01-200x200.jpg 200w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/dusty-pink-tile-240525-1040-01-768x768.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/dusty-pink-tile-240525-1040-01-1536x1536.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePalette by Flaviker\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1738\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/green-tile-bathroom-240525-1040-01.jpg\" alt=\" Soft sage green tiles meet a tropical leaf-print wallpaper in this dreamy, nature-inspired bathroom. The vertical tile layout adds height, while the fluted basin brings an artisan touch, perfect for a calming, curated space with personality.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/green-tile-bathroom-240525-1040-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/green-tile-bathroom-240525-1040-01-940x851.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/green-tile-bathroom-240525-1040-01-800x724.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/green-tile-bathroom-240525-1040-01-768x695.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/green-tile-bathroom-240525-1040-01-1536x1390.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePorcelain Stoneware in Tropical and Aloe by FAP Ceramiche\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blue-tiles-bathroom-240525-1041-01.jpg\" alt=\" Layers of turquoise and deep ocean blue tiles bring coastal calm to this sunlit bathroom. The open view, organic textures, and sleek sink design create a fresh, resort-inspired space perfect for everyday escapes.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blue-tiles-bathroom-240525-1041-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blue-tiles-bathroom-240525-1041-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blue-tiles-bathroom-240525-1041-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blue-tiles-bathroom-240525-1041-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blue-tiles-bathroom-240525-1041-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eSinfonia by Ceramica Bardelli\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1875\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/grey-bathroom-tiles-240525-1041-01.jpg\" alt=\" Minimalist and moody, this walk-in shower features smooth grey tiles and a striking stone bench that adds texture and drama. The matte black fixtures complete the clean, architectural look with effortless sophistication.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/grey-bathroom-tiles-240525-1041-01.jpg 1500w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/grey-bathroom-tiles-240525-1041-01-940x1175.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/grey-bathroom-tiles-240525-1041-01-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/grey-bathroom-tiles-240525-1041-01-768x960.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/grey-bathroom-tiles-240525-1041-01-1229x1536.jpg 1229w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eColovers+ in Love Avio by Supergres\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/green-bathroom-tiles-240525-1041-01.jpg\" alt=\"This refreshing bathroom blends rustic wood, glossy green tiles, and natural textures to create a serene oasis. The open shower and leafy accents make it feel like a spa retreat tucked inside a tropical courtyard.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/green-bathroom-tiles-240525-1041-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/green-bathroom-tiles-240525-1041-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/green-bathroom-tiles-240525-1041-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/green-bathroom-tiles-240525-1041-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/green-bathroom-tiles-240525-1041-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eLook Tiles in Turchese Glossy and Turchese Struttura 3B Yubi Glossy by RAGNO\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003e2. Anthroform: Tiles with Soul\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eDesign meets storytelling in the “Anthroform” movement, a shift toward tiles that celebrate humanity, heritage, and handcraft. Italian tilemakers are collaborating with top designers and sourcing from the land itself, reimagining age-old materials and cultural motifs through a contemporary lens.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2264\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-blue-tiles-240525-1106-01.jpg\" alt=\" This geometric wall tile brings depth and movement to any space with its hand-painted square pattern and moody blue-gray tones. A minimalist chair and raw concrete add to the gallery-like atmosphere.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-blue-tiles-240525-1106-01.jpg 1600w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-blue-tiles-240525-1106-01-940x1330.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-blue-tiles-240525-1106-01-800x1132.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-blue-tiles-240525-1106-01-768x1087.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-blue-tiles-240525-1106-01-1086x1536.jpg 1086w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-blue-tiles-240525-1106-01-1447x2048.jpg 1447w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eOLTRENERO by Mirago\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2400\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1108-01.jpg\" alt=\" A striking play of repetition and contrast, this terracotta-and-white mosaic tile adds a graphic punch to contemporary interiors. Perfect for statement walls where texture meets precision.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1108-01.jpg 1600w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1108-01-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1108-01-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1108-01-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1108-01-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1108-01-1365x2048.jpg 1365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eFlicker by Decoratori Bassanesi\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2380\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1107-01.jpg\" alt=\" This tranquil bedroom blends soft terracotta and sandy tones in striated tile walls that mimic natural sediment. Perfect for earthy interiors that embrace calm, texture, and modern minimalism.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1107-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1107-01-940x1165.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1107-01-800x992.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1107-01-768x952.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1107-01-1239x1536.jpg 1239w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1107-01-1652x2048.jpg 1652w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eBioterre by Del Conca\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1107-02.jpg\" alt=\" A striking mix of matte textures and graphic patterns, these contemporary tiles play with circles and diamonds in a rich ochre palette. A perfect statement surface for moody kitchens, coffee nooks, or modern hospitality spaces.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1107-02.jpg 1600w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1107-02-940x635.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1107-02-800x540.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1107-02-768x518.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tiles-240525-1107-02-1536x1037.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eMOTIF by Leonardo Ceramics\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2133\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-blue-grey-bathroom-tiles-240525-1107-01.jpg\" alt=\"Vertical brushstroke stripes in cool-toned tile bring rhythm and calm to this skylit bathroom. A seamless flow from wall to floor adds a spa-like touch to the pared-back, monochrome design.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-blue-grey-bathroom-tiles-240525-1107-01.jpg 1600w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-blue-grey-bathroom-tiles-240525-1107-01-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-blue-grey-bathroom-tiles-240525-1107-01-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-blue-grey-bathroom-tiles-240525-1107-01-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-blue-grey-bathroom-tiles-240525-1107-01-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-blue-grey-bathroom-tiles-240525-1107-01-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePoetry Stone Reloaded and Alterego Milk by ABK\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003e3. Art Deco Revival\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe glamour is back. Art Deco is striding boldly into tile design, bringing dramatic geometry, opulent finishes, and vintage vibes with a modern twist. From checkerboard patterns to monochrome statements, these tiles are perfect for those who want bold elegance with a sense of nostalgia.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1837\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-01.jpg\" alt=\"These organic tiles in green and blue create a rhythmic, high-impact floor moment. Perfect for adding depth and personality to a muted living space with a hint of vintage elegance.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-01.jpg 1837w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-01-940x1310.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-01-800x1115.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-01-768x1070.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-01-1102x1536.jpg 1102w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-01-1470x2048.jpg 1470w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1837px) 100vw, 1837px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003e14 Ora Italiana by ABK\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-02.jpg\" alt=\"Bold, angular tiles bring sculptural drama to this neutral-toned bathroom. The geometric pattern plays with light and shadow, creating a dynamic backdrop for minimalist fixtures and a softly curved mirror. A confident choice for elevating everyday rituals.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-02-940x940.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-02-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-02-200x200.jpg 200w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-02-768x768.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-02-1536x1536.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eTerrae by Casalgrande Padana\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1858\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-03.jpg\" alt=\"Clean lines and soft contrast define this tile design, where warm wood tones intersect over cool concrete grey. The subtle grid pattern brings quiet order to contemporary spaces, perfectly pairing with light oak furniture and sculptural decor.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-03.jpg 1500w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-03-940x1164.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-03-800x991.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-03-768x951.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-03-1240x1536.jpg 1240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eSensoria by Del Conca\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2337\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-04.jpg\" alt=\"Classic checkerboard tile gets an elevated twist with deep burgundy and soft ivory marbling. The high-contrast floor grounds this arched, Mediterranean-inspired space with quiet drama, adding a sense of timeless elegance to minimalist interiors.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-04.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-04-940x1144.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-04-800x974.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-04-768x935.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-04-1262x1536.jpg 1262w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-04-1683x2048.jpg 1683w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eMajestic by LaFenice\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2337\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-05.jpg\" alt=\"Green-veined marble tiles bordered in a grid layout offer a fresh, tailored take on traditional checkerboard floors. Paired with classic panelled walls and midcentury dining pieces, this patterned tile adds structure and quiet luxury to a soft-toned dining room.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-05.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-05-940x1144.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-05-800x974.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-05-768x935.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-05-1262x1536.jpg 1262w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-05-1683x2048.jpg 1683w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eGlazed porcelain tiles by Verde1999\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2221\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-06.jpg\" alt=\"This luxurious bathroom floor blends warm-toned marble with an intricate geometric tile pattern that feels both Art Deco and fashion-forward. The soft gold accents, sculptural sink design, and branded towels elevate the space into a curated moment of glamour.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-06.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-06-940x1087.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-06-800x925.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-06-768x888.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-06-1328x1536.jpg 1328w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/art-deco-inspired-tiles-240525-1127-06-1770x2048.jpg 1770w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eTarsia by Versace Ceramics\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003e4. Lightscape: Playing with Glow\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eTiles that capture and reflect light are turning walls and floors into glowing canvases. This year’s collections are all about how light moves across a surface, changing as the sun shifts, the lights dim, or the shadows fall. The effect is a space that feels alive, dynamic, and radiant without a single bulb changing.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2066\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-01.jpg\" alt=\"Soft curves, peachy pink tones, and a mix of matte and glossy finishes give these wall tiles a playful retro vibe. Perfect for a backsplash or accent wall that nods to the 70s while feeling fresh and curated.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-01.jpg 2066w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-01-940x1165.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-01-800x991.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-01-768x952.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-01-1240x1536.jpg 1240w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-01-1653x2048.jpg 1653w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2066px) 100vw, 2066px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eManufatti by Faetano\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1279\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-02.jpg\" alt=\"A soft neutral palette meets retro-inspired geometry in these floor tiles, combining a subtle sheen with rounded square motifs. Ideal for creating a relaxed, modern look with just the right amount of vintage charm.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-02-940x626.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-02-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-02-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-02-1536x1023.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePottery Stone Reloaded by ABK\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1356\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-03.jpg\" alt=\"This dramatic stone bar creates a showstopping centerpiece with its iridescent blues, greens, and flashes of gold. Perfect for bold interiors where luxury meets natural spectacle.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-03.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-03-940x664.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-03-800x565.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-03-768x542.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/contemporary-tile-240525-1145-03-1536x1085.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003eTele di Marmo Lumia by Emilceramica\u003c/h6\u0